{
  "stem": "23942.4",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "It's very possible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And those maluchem were guiding me and protecting me from that nothing bad should happen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "That's the only way I can explain it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Because there was no way I could have been that smart that I could've avoided the Germans I saw in the street and Poles that saw me and some of them knew I was Jewish and didn't give me away.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "All this, there was-- it's impossible this should have happened with all this my doing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "I believe there was a maluch, either one or two, and guiding me and protecting me that I should survive.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And that's the only way I can explain it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "What I did, I did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "But to have that much protection that nothing should have happened to me against all odds.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "I walked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "I was visible, and nobody ever arrested me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And I can tell you incident that there is no way that I could have been not protected about without supernatural help.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "There's no way.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "I cannot forget that this could have happened any other way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I thought-- should I mention that incident?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One day-- you see, one day there was-- it happened that not far where I was in the edge of the woods by this lady with the two daughters that one day the Nazis-- the Nazi, because there was only one.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He came and somebody reported there were Jewish hiding, Jewish people hiding in this house where it was like all alone in the woods, almost like the edge of the woods.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was actually in the woods, not deep in the woods, but there was woods surrounding.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she was very primitive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The house had a thatched roof and there was a log cabin there.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
